Beth,

It is *very* easy to get the cover off the seat and soak it.  It also
washes in a machine quite well with no detectable shrinkage  Getting the
sugar out of the foam/horshair may be worse (*don't* soap the horsehair
(if you have any left)), but it is sugar, and thus water soluble.

